nd, I&#39;d still wonder if the &quot;Long  Range&quot; is  the better option here. </span></div></div>", "forwarded_html": ""}, {"id": "1428818614923825213", "author": "John", "author_handle": "john_52700", "user_id": "1317203749286056096", "avatar": "", "timestamp": "Friday, October 17, 2025 2:55 p.m.", "timestamp_short": "2025-10-17 2:55 p.m.", "text": "That's good news, thanks Tyler", "content_html": "<div class=\"chatlog__content chatlog__markdown\"><span class=chatlog__markdown-preserve>That&#39;s good news, thanks Tyler</span></div>", "embeds_html": [], "attachments_html": [], "reactions_html": "", "reply_html": "", "forwarded_html": ""}, {"id": "1428818760982335589", "author": "Tyler - OlneyLoftBase", "author_handle": "livthedream83", "user_id": "178637537655390208", "avatar": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/guilds/1343693475589263471/users/178637537655390208/avatars/a_0d844f5a01b57555a241ec580723c07f.gif?size=512", "timestamp": "Friday, October 17, 2025 2:55 p.m.", "timestamp_short": "2025-10-17 2:55 p.m.", "text": "Hope you get some contacts soon. Suggest you contact your local HAM radio groups and maker spaces.", "content_html": "<div class=\"chatlog__content chatlog__markdown\"><span class=chatlog__markdown-preserve>Hope you get some contacts soon. Suggest you contact your local HAM radio groups and maker spaces.</span></div>", "embeds_html": [], "attachments_html": [], "reactions_html": "", "reply_html": "<div class=chatlog__reply><img class=chatlog__reply-avatar src=https://cdn.discordapp.com/embed/avatars/0.png alt=Avatar loading=lazy><div class=chatlog__reply-author title=john_52700>John</div><div class=chatlog__reply-content><span class=chatlog__reply-link onclick=\"scrollToMessage(event,'1428818614923825213')\"> That&#39;s good news, thanks Tyler </span></div></div>", "forwarded_html": ""}, {"id": "1429109433681838236", "author": "John", "author_handle": "john_52700", "user_id": "1317203749286056096", "avatar": "", "timestamp": "Saturday, October 18, 2