 </span></div></div>", "forwarded_html": ""}, {"id": "1429124351579390065", "author": "John", "author_handle": "john_52700", "user_id": "1317203749286056096", "avatar": "", "timestamp": "Saturday, October 18, 2025 11:09 a.m.", "timestamp_short": "2025-10-18 11:09 a.m.", "text": "It's quite some distance to Estonia, and not too many other Finnish stations (yet?)", "content_html": "<div class=\"chatlog__content chatlog__markdown\"><span class=chatlog__markdown-preserve>It&#39;s quite some distance to Estonia, and not too many other Finnish stations (yet?)</span></div>", "embeds_html": [], "attachments_html": [], "reactions_html": "", "reply_html": "", "forwarded_html": ""}, {"id": "1429127955560402944", "author": "Tyler - OlneyLoftBase", "author_handle": "livthedream83", "user_id": "178637537655390208", "avatar": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/guilds/1343693475589263471/users/178637537655390208/avatars/a_0d844f5a01b57555a241ec580723c07f.gif?size=512", "timestamp": "Saturday, October 18, 2025 11:24 a.m.", "timestamp_short": "2025-10-18 11:24 a.m.", "text": "Consider reaching out via FB to the lcoal HAM radio groups", "content_html": "<div class=\"chatlog__content chatlog__markdown\"><span class=chatlog__markdown-preserve>Consider reaching out via FB to the lcoal HAM radio groups</span></div>", "embeds_html": [], "attachments_html": [], "reactions_html": "", "reply_html": "<div class=chatlog__reply><img class=chatlog__reply-avatar src=https://cdn.discordapp.com/embed/avatars/0.png alt=Avatar loading=lazy><div class=chatlog__reply-author title=john_52700>John</div><div class=chatlog__reply-content><span class=chatlog__reply-link onclick=\"scrollToMessage(event,'1429124351579390065')\"> It&#39;s quite some distance to Estonia, and not too many other Finnish stations (yet?) </span></div></div>", "forwarded_html": ""}, {"id": "1429128251426471947", "author": "John", "author_handle": "john_52700", "user_id": "1317203749286056096", "avatar": "", "timestamp": "Saturday, October 18, 2025 11:25 a.m.", "timestamp_short": "2025-10-18 11:25 a.m.", "text": "FB I use the local FM repeater instead hihi, I guess eventually we'll see more in Finland.", "content_html": "<div class=\"chatlog__content chatlog__markdown\"><span class=chatlog__markdown-preserve>FB <img\n    loading=\"lazy\"\n    class=\"chatlog__emoji \"\n    alt=\"🙂\"\n    title=\"slight_smile\"\n    src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/twitter/twemoji@latest/assets/svg/1f642.svg\"> I use the local FM repeater instead hihi,  I guess eventually we&#39;ll see more in Finland.</span></div>", "embeds_html": [], "attachments_html": [], "reactions_html": "", "reply_html": "", "forwarded_html": ""}, {"id": "1433169922753564733", "author": "Xinayder", "author_handle": "xinayder", "user_id": "90593466450481152", "avatar": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/avatars/90593466450481152/f2debce1c0145cedc47efc68fdfc4202.png?size=512", "timestamp": "Wednesday, October 29, 2025 3:05 p.m.", "timestamp_short": "2025-10-29 3:05 p.m.", "text": "I travelled to Finland last week, was sad to not get my messages heard by any repeater. I drove from Helsinki to Turku and nothing. the official meshcore map showed only 2 nodes connected to the grid, and they were running the older, non-narrow band setting.", "content_html": "<div class=\"chatlog__content chatlog__markdown\"><span class=chatlog__markdown-preserve>I travelled to Finland last week, was sad to not get my messages heard by any repeater. I drove from Helsinki to Turku and nothing. the official meshcore map showed only 2 nodes connected to the grid, and they were running the older, non-narrow band setting.</span></div>", "embeds_html": [], "attachments_html": [], "reactions_html": "", "reply_html": "", "forwarded_html": ""}, {"id": "1433539563418288128", "author": "John", "author_handle": "john_52700", "user_id": "1317203749286056096", "avatar": "", "timestamp": "Thursday, October 30, 2025 3:34 p.m.", "timestamp_short": "2025-10-30 3:34 p.m.", "text": "Hey, yes Finland has not seen much activity yet, lately 2 repeaters were added, with the 'narrow' setting. Hope you had a good time nevertheless!", "content_html": "<div class=\"chatlog__content chatlog__markdown\"><span class=chatlog__markdown-preserve>Hey, yes Finland has not seen much activity yet, lately 2 repeaters were added, with the &#39;narrow&#39; setting. Hope you had a good time nevertheless!</span></div>", "embeds_html": [], "attachments_html": [], "reactions_html": "", "reply_html": "", "forwarded_html": ""}, {"id": "1463243169914421291", "author": "Chain", "author_handle": "chain2033", "user_id": "207206831603318784", "avatar": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/avatars/207206831603318784/294d5279c7f4657f232b270dbd8c7a5a.png?size=512", "timestamp": "Tuesday, January 20, 2026 1:45 p.m.", "timestamp_short": "2026-01-20 1:45 p.m.", "text": "Hi guys! New to Meshcore. I'm located in Finland. Do I need to set up any other settings than EU/UK (Narrow)?", "content_html": "<div class=\"chatlog__content chatlog__markdown\"><span class=chatlog__markdown-preserve>Hi guys! New to Meshcore. I&#39;m located in Finland. Do I need to set up any other settings than EU/UK (Narrow)?</span></div>", "embeds_html": [], "attachments_html": [], "reactions_html": "", "reply_html": "", "forwarded_html": ""}, {"id": "1463255365411147889", "author": "Chain", "author_handle": "chain2033", "user_id": "207206831603318784", "avatar": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/avatars/207206831603318784/294d5279c7f4657f232b270dbd8c7a5a.png?size=512", "timestamp": "Tuesday, January 20, 2026 2:34 p.m.", "timestamp_short": "2026-01-20 2:34 p.m.", "text": "Hmm that preset seems to set 869.62, BW 62, CR4/8", "content_html": "<div class=\"chatlog__content chatlog__markdown\"><span class=chatlog__markdown-preserve>Hmm that preset seems to set 869.62, BW 62, CR4/8</span></div>", "embeds_html": [], "attachments_html": [], "reactions_html": "", "reply_html": "", "forwarded_html": ""}, {"id": "1463265302732345478", "author": "Chain", "author_handle": "chain2033", "user_id": "207206831603318784", "avatar": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/avatars/207206831603318784/294d5279c7f4657f232b270dbd8c7a5a.png?size=512", "timestamp": "Tuesday, January 20, 2026 3:13 p.m.", "timestamp_short": "2026-01-20 3:13 p.m.", "text": "Interesting. I set up a T-1000E and used phone to set the correct settings. Seems that messages can be sent between devices. Pehaps MeshOS just is buggy and does not display correct settings in the System info screen. Or the settings are close enough so messages go through.", "content_html": "<div class=\"chatlog__content chatlog__markdown\"><span class=chatlog__markdown-preserve>Interesting. I set up a T-1000E and used phone to set the correct settings. Seems that messages can be sent between devices. Pehaps MeshOS just is buggy and does not display correct settings in the System info screen. Or the settings are close enough so messages go through.</span></div>", "embeds_html": [], "attachments_html": [], "reactions_html": "", "reply_html": "", "forwarded_html": ""}, {"id": "1463266902263595182", "author": "Tyler - OlneyLoftBase", "author_handle": "livthedream83", "user_id": "178637537655390208", "avatar": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/guilds/1343693475589263471/users/178637537655390208/avatars/a_0d844f5a01b57555a241ec580723c07f.gif?size=512", "timestamp": "Tuesday, January 20, 2026 3:20 p.m.", "timestamp_short": "2026-01-20 3:20 p.m.", "text": "Whole of europe uses UK/EU Narrow right nwo theres not many of you so you might be alone for a bit", "content_html": "<div class=\"chatlog__content chatlog__markdown\"><span class=chatlog__markdown-preserve>Whole of europe uses UK/EU Narrow right nwo theres not many of you so you might be alone for a bit</span></div>", "embeds_html": [], "attachments_html": [], "reactions_html": "", "reply_html": "<div class=chatlog__reply><img class=chatlog__reply-avatar src=\"https://cdn.discordapp.com/avatars/207206831603318784/294d5279c7f4657f232b270dbd8c7a5a